Executive Profile
John E. McGlade  Chairman, Chief Executive Officer and President, Air Products Singapore Pte. Ltd.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 3 Board Members in 3 different organizations across 4 different industries.See Board Relationships63--
Background

		Mr. John E. McGlade has been the Chief Executive Officer and President of Air Products Singapore Pte. Ltd. since October 2007. Mr. McGlade focuses on setting the strategy and policies of Air Products, developing leadership and meeting shareholder commitments. He served as the Chief Executive Officer of Air Products & Chemicals Inc. from October 1, 2007 to July 1, 2014. He served as President of Air Products & Chemicals Inc., from October 1, 2006 to July 1, 2014. He served ... as a Group Vice President of Chemicals, Group Business Divisions of Air Products & Chemicals Inc., from November 1, 2003 to October 1, 2006. He was responsible for the global Chemicals organization of Air Products, including the Performance Materials and Industrial Chemicals Divisions and international chemicals commercial operations in Asia, Europe and Latin America. He served as the Chief Operating Officer of Air Products & Chemicals Inc. since October 1, 2006. Mr. McGlade joined Air Products in 1976 as a Participant in Air Products' Career Development Program and held various positions within the Industrial Gases Division, including both domestic and international assignments. He served as General Manager of the Chemical and Process Industries Division of Air Products' Career Development Program since 1994 and served as its Vice President of the Division since 1996. Mr. McGlade served as Vice President and General Manager of Chemical and Process Industries, Energy Systems since 1998, Vice President and General Manager of Performance Materials Division since 2001 and served as Vice President of Chemicals Group business divisions since 2003. He has been Chairman of the Board of Air Products Singapore Pte. Ltd. since April 2008. He served as the Chairman of Air Products & Chemicals Inc., from April 1, 2008 to July 1, 2014. He has been a Director of The Goodyear Tire & Rubber Company since December 5, 2012 and Independent Director of Bunge Limited since August 5, 2014. He served as a Director of Air Products & Chemicals Inc., since May 17, 2007. He is a Director of the American Chemistry Council. He is a Member of the Society of Chemical Industry. He is a Member of the Lehigh University Board of Trustees. Mr. McGlade holds a BS in Industrial Engineering from Lehigh University and an MBA from Lehigh University.Read Full Background




